text: Nikolskoye () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Nikolsky Selsoviet of Yenotayevsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 5,234 as of 2010. There are 62 streets. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yenotayevsky District
title: Nikolskoye, Yenotayevsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
